WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:13.040 --> 00:00:17.920
Nearly 75% of women across the world are prone to yeast infection

00:00:18.180 --> 00:00:21.960
or Candida infection, named after the fungus that causes it.

00:00:22.840 --> 00:00:26.660
This infection is quite common, particularly among women.

00:00:27.340 --> 00:00:31.820
The growth of yeast cells leads to infection which causes itching,

00:00:31.860 --> 00:00:35.840
burning or swelling in and around the affected area.

00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:43.420
It can also occur as oral thrush or localized skin fold infection
 under the breasts and lower abdomen.

00:00:44.580 --> 00:00:48.300
Yeast infection could also develop due to factors such as:

00:00:48.300 --> 00:00:53.180
Use of antibiotics, Hormonal fluctuation, especially during pregnancy,

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:59.440
Weakened immune system and Endocrine disorders such
 as thyroid disorder and diabetes.

00:01:00.080 --> 00:01:05.260
But before you panic and rush to consult a doctor, try some natural and safe home remedies.

00:01:09.360 --> 00:01:13.780
Probiotics help rebuild the body's defence mechanism against yeast.

00:01:14.300 --> 00:01:19.080
So eat generous quantity of yogurt every day, particularly in the morning.

00:01:19.620 --> 00:01:23.680
You can also dip a cotton ball in plain yogurt 

00:01:24.500 --> 00:01:26.980
and apply it on the affected area.

00:01:27.260 --> 00:01:30.240
Leave it overnight or for at least 20-30 minutes.

00:01:35.240 --> 00:01:39.440
The next remedy that can be used to protect yourself against yeast infection.

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:43.020
For this remedy you need coconut oil.

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:47.860
Rinse the affected area thoroughly
 and then apply the coconut oil.

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:51.580
This remedy can be used in the genital area, too.

00:01:51.580 --> 00:01:57.820
In case of oral thrush, simply swish the coconut oil
 in your mouth for about 5-10 minutes.

00:01:58.500 --> 00:02:01.400
And repeat this for at least three times a day.

00:02:06.060 --> 00:02:10.100
The next remedy that I am going  to tell you
 to protect yourself against yeast infection.

00:02:10.680 --> 00:02:16.560
For this remedy we need
 a cup of warm water and apple cider vinegar.

00:02:18.040 --> 00:02:20.500
Take 2 tablespoons of apple cider vinegar.

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:26.140
Mix the solution thoroughly.

00:02:29.880 --> 00:02:31.860
And drink this solution twice a day.

00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:35.680
Tips to help you further in dealing with yeast infection.

00:02:36.380 --> 00:02:41.820
Yeast feeds on sugar. So, avoid having sugary foods
 and beverages, Avoid alcohol, too.

00:02:42.520 --> 00:02:44.500
Eat 2-3 garlic cloves a day.

00:02:45.080 --> 00:02:47.220
And drink unsweetened cranberry juice.

